title: Unsolved Mysteries + Georgie Porgie, Ride the Snake - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/22
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a special episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason investigate a handful of “Unsolved Mysteries” through two weeks!  Plus, the Week 3 edition of Buy or Sell, and a Thursday Night Football preview of the Panthers vs Texans. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 22nd, 2021
  
 (04:30) - Buy or Sell
 (11:35) - NFL News 
 (24:20) - Unsolved Mysteries
 (24:45) - Rob Gronkowski
 (30:45) - Ezekiel Elliott & Tony Pollard
 (36:45) - Carolina & Washington Defenses
 (42:55) - Clyde Edwards-Helaire
 (50:20) - Las Vegas Raiders
 (56:00) - Thursday Night Breakdown - Panthers at Texans
